headline: Viking Q2 Earnings Meet Estimates, Revenues Beat, Both Rise Y/Y
summary: VIK's second-quarter 2025 revenues benefit from increased Capacity Passenger Cruise Days (capacity PCDs), higher Occupancy and higher revenue per PCD.
